This paper is primarily focused on natural language processing and machine learning, which suggests that it would likely fall under the cs.CL (Computation and Language) sub-category. Additionally, the paper discusses the ability of people to learn and generalize new concepts, which is a key area of research in artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and machine learning (cs.LG). The paper also includes experiments that involve image recognition, which could place it in the cs.CV (Computer Vision) sub-category. Finally, the paper discusses cognitive modeling, which could potentially place it in the cs.CC (Computational Complexity) sub-category.
